B.aV3=new A.a_(B.N4,["PARTE TRES \u2014 Cinco acciones para elevar SCS y PROGRESIVO ({agent})","PARTE TRES \u2014 Cinco acciones para inclinar PROGRESIVO ({agent})","Como {agent} responsable, oriente {subject} hacia transporte de cohesi\xf3n PROGRESIVO \u2014 los l\xedderes establecidos deben perseguir siempre resultados constructivos que generen confianza.","SCS objetivo: {current} \u2192 {min}\u2013{max}","Hacia PROGRESIVO: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}% transporte regresivo","Transporte PROGRESIVO: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}%","Previsto: SCS sube hacia {min}\u2013{max} en EL CONTINUUM.","Estas cinco acciones usan puntuaciones Chronoflux \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc, inclinaci\xf3n del continuo, tasas base del registro y proyecciones de palancas de PARTE TRES para inclinar EL CONTINUUM hacia PROGRESIVO.","{lean} \xb7 {region} \xb7 {reg}% regresivo / {prog}% progresivo \xb7 {subject}","Publicar datos verificados y diferenciados sobre {subject}.","Reducir fricci\xf3n \u03c3/I\u03c4 con seguimiento transparente.","Fortalecer transporte de confianza J\u03bc entre grupos.","Apuntar al constructo de mayor fricci\xf3n (\u03c3 o I\u03c4) con hitos medibles de desescalada en {subject}.","Publicar revisi\xf3n de responsabilidad PROGRESIVA con hitos publicados vinculando palancas a ganancias de SCS en {subject}.","{agent}: Reducir polarizaci\xf3n \u03c3 en {subject} \u2014 convocar foro multipartidista en 14 d\xedas. {hook} (\u03c3 {scs}/100, {weight}% peso Chronoflux; {reg}% continuo regresivo).","{agent}: Reducir arrastre institucional I\u03c4 en {subject} \u2014 publicar cronolog\xedas de decisi\xf3n y revisiones independientes. {hook} (I\u03c4 {scs}/100, {weight}% peso).","{agent}: Fortalecer transporte de confianza J\u03bc en {subject} \u2014 alcance diferenciado a segmentos de baja confianza. {hook} (J\u03bc {scs}/100, {weight}% peso; objetivo impulso PROGRESIVO desde {prog}% cuota progresiva).","{agent}: Reencuadrar el v\xf3rtice \u03c9 en {subject} \u2014 rueda de prensa basada en evidencia separando hechos verificados de compresi\xf3n narrativa. {hook} (\u03c9 {scs}/100).","Anclar a variable \u03c9 suministrada: \xab{text}\xbb.","Encuadre \u03c9 inferido de la pregunta planteada (SCS {scs}/100).","{agent}: Comprometer revisi\xf3n de responsabilidad PROGRESIVA con hitos publicados para {subject} \u2014 mover EL CONTINUUM de {reg}% regresivo / {prog}% progresivo (SCS refinado {refined}/100 \u2192 {min}\u2013{max} con palancas vs {without} sin; calibrado {pct}%; {n} casos de registro al {base}% tasa base; momento {momentum}).","Acci\xf3n de discurso del escenario \u2014 {theme} Apunta a {construct} para construir transporte PROGRESIVO.","Palanca basada en datos sobre {construct} ({scs}/100, {weight}% peso Chronoflux) \u2014 reduce fricci\xf3n del {reg}% regresivo hacia transporte PROGRESIVO.","Integra continuo ({reg}%/{prog}%), SCS refinado {refined}/100, calibrado {pct}% y {n} casos de registro \u2014 cierre de responsabilidad institucional.","{agent}: Publicar datos verificados de incidentes sobre {subject}.","{agent}: Convocar enlace comunitario en 14 d\xedas.","{agent}: Desplegar un registro p\xfablico de cumplimiento.","{agent}: Emitir respuesta basada en evidencia sobre {subject}.","{agent}: Convocar rueda de prensa abierta sobre {subject}.","{agent}: Encargar revisi\xf3n de mensajes a 30 d\xedas.","{agent}: Publicar tablas de impacto de costos sobre {subject}.","{agent}: Mediar negociaci\xf3n con partes interesadas.","{agent}: Anunciar hitos de alivio por fases.","{agent}: Publicar hoja de afirmaciones vs. registros.","{agent}: Organizar foro p\xfablico neutral sobre {subject}.","{agent}: Publicar cronolog\xedas listas para auditor\xeda.","{agent}: Publicar mapa narrativo correctivo sobre {subject}.","{agent}: Convocar intercambio estructurado de evidencia.","{agent}: Desplegar alcance de confianza diferenciado.","{agent}: Convocar rueda de prensa abierta con criterios de decisi\xf3n.","{agent}: Encargar revisi\xf3n independiente del proceso.","{agent}: Fijar fechas de revisi\xf3n p\xfablicas vinculantes.","{agent}: Convocar sesi\xf3n p\xfablica anclada a {subject}.","{agent}: Mapear posiciones de partes desde entradas \u03c3/I\u03c4.","{agent}: Publicar pr\xf3ximos pasos con plazo."],t.w)
B.aV4=new A.a_(B.N4,["PART THREE \u2014 Five actions to raise SCS & PROGRESSIVE ({agent})","PART THREE \u2014 Five actions to shift PROGRESSIVE ({agent})","As the accountable {agent}, steer {subject} toward PROGRESSIVE cohesion transport \u2014 establishment leaders should always pursue constructive, trust-building outcomes.","Target SCS: {current} \u2192 {min}\u2013{max}","Shift toward PROGRESSIVE: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}% regressive transport","Build PROGRESSIVE transport: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}%","Expected: SCS rises toward {min}\u2013{max} on THE CONTINUUM.","These five actions use Chronoflux \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc scores, continuum lean, registry base rates, and PART THREE lever projections to shift THE CONTINUUM PROGRESSIVE.","{lean} \xb7 {region} \xb7 {reg}% regressive / {prog}% progressive \xb7 {subject}","Publish verified, differentiated data on {subject}.","Cut \u03c3/I\u03c4 friction with transparent follow-through.","Strengthen J\u03bc trust transport across groups.","Target the highest-friction construct (\u03c3 or I\u03c4) with measurable de-escalation milestones on {subject}.","Publish a PROGRESSIVE accountability review with published milestones tying lever use to SCS gains on {subject}.","{agent}: Cut \u03c3 polarisation on {subject} \u2014 convene a multi-stakeholder forum within 14 days. {hook} (\u03c3 {scs}/100, {weight}% Chronoflux weight; {reg}% regressive continuum).","{agent}: Reduce I\u03c4 institutional drag on {subject} \u2014 publish decision timelines and independent review triggers. {hook} (I\u03c4 {scs}/100, {weight}% weight).","{agent}: Strengthen J\u03bc trust transport on {subject} \u2014 differentiated outreach to low-trust segments. {hook} (J\u03bc {scs}/100, {weight}% weight; target PROGRESSIVE lift from {prog}% progressive share).","{agent}: Reframe the \u03c9 vortex on {subject} \u2014 evidence-first briefing separating verified facts from narrative compression. {hook} (\u03c9 {scs}/100).",'Anchor to supplied \u03c9 variable: "{text}".',"Inferred \u03c9 framing from posed question (SCS {scs}/100).","{agent}: Commit to a PROGRESSIVE accountability review with published milestones for {subject} \u2014 shift THE CONTINUUM from {reg}% regressive / {prog}% progressive (refined SCS {refined}/100 \u2192 {min}\u2013{max} with levers vs {without} without; calibrated {pct}%; {n} registry cases at {base}% base rate; momentum {momentum}).","Scenario discourse action \u2014 {theme} Targets {construct} to build PROGRESSIVE transport.","Data-driven lever on {construct} ({scs}/100, {weight}% Chronoflux weight) \u2014 reduces friction from {reg}% regressive toward PROGRESSIVE transport.","Integrates continuum ({reg}%/{prog}%), refined SCS {refined}/100, calibrated {pct}%, and {n} registry cases \u2014 establishment accountability capstone.","{agent}: Publish verified incident data for {subject}.","{agent}: Convene community liaison within 14 days.","{agent}: Deploy a public compliance tracker.","{agent}: Issue an evidence-based response on {subject}.","{agent}: Hold an open press Q&A on {subject}.","{agent}: Commission a 30-day messaging review.","{agent}: Publish cost-impact tables for {subject}.","{agent}: Broker a timed stakeholder negotiation.","{agent}: Announce phased relief milestones.","{agent}: Release a claims-vs-records fact sheet.","{agent}: Host a neutral public forum on {subject}.","{agent}: Publish audit-ready decision timelines.","{agent}: Publish a corrective narrative map on {subject}.","{agent}: Hold a structured evidence exchange.","{agent}: Deploy differentiated trust outreach.","{agent}: Hold an open briefing with published decision criteria.","{agent}: Commission an independent process review.","{agent}: Set binding public review dates.","{agent}: Convene a public session anchored to {subject}.","{agent}: Map stakeholder positions from \u03c3/I\u03c4 inputs.","{agent}: Publish time-bound next steps."],t.w)
